# Cross-Origin Isolation headers required by @webcontainer/api.
# Scoped to /builder/* so that the rest of the app (auth, dashboard,
# Google avatars, GitHub OAuth popup) keeps working without crossorigin
# attribute changes.
#
# These apply on Lovable's preview hosting (Cloudflare Workers) and on
# Netlify production deployments — both honor `public/_headers`.
/builder/*
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: require-corp
  Cross-Origin-Resource-Policy: cross-origin